thread.title: Aid workers hit by airstrike in Eastern Ghouta: Social media video

title: Aid workers hit by airstrike in Eastern Ghouta: Social media video
text:
Aid workers hit by airstrike in Eastern Ghouta: Social media video   01:19 
Syrian government forces gained more ground in an assault on eastern Ghouta near Damascus on Saturday, a day after aid workers were purportedly hit by airstrikes. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
